        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Stop Illicit Drug Importation Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act to expand the authority of the Food and Drug Administration to prohibit the importation of certain drugs or destroy illegally imported or hazardous drugs.</p>]]></text>
